<p>But viewers appeared distracted by the ice cream entrepreneur's good looks, with one person commented: 'This Scott guys Instagram is going to be blowing up tonight all those thirsty gays and housewives.'</p>

<p>Meanwhile others speculated that Scott, who will return to the show tonight, is the mystery contestant who producers have teased will secure themselves the top prize of £1,000,000 this week.</p>

